'''Ken Steacy''' is a renowned [[Star Wars comic books|comic]] artist from [[Wikipedia:Canada|Canada]]. His artwork is featured on the covers of [[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine 1|''Star Wars Galaxy'' #1]] and ''[[The Art of Star Wars Galaxy]]''. He also provided the illustrations for ''[[Podracing Tales]]'', ''[[Imperial Spy]]'', and ''[[R2-D2's Mission: A Little Hero's Journey]]''.

